  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Crew Packs\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about Star Atlas crew packs.\nSTAR ATLAS: THE ROAD AHEAD\nAephia published an article about the Star Atlas roadmap.\nSTAR ATLAS ROADMAP UPDATE 2024 (First Look & Commentary)\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about the Star Atlas roadmap.\nMetaverse Nomads #139 w/ @Virtuwul | ROME – Star Atlas Rainbow Phi Owner\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video replay of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nStar Atlas New SURGE Showroom Reaction!\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the new Showroom version with SURGE.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #122\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nAnnouncing “Starbased” — A New Chapter in the Star Atlas SAGE Saga\nStar Atlas published an article about the new version of SAGE.\nThe Atlas Brew #104\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nSTAR ATLAS #226 STARBASSED ANNOUNCED, WHAT YOU NEED TO DO!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video going over the SAGE Starbased announcement.\nStar Atlas Recap 3-28-24\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping the latest in Star Atlas.\nAtlas Brew #104: Community Updates – TLDR\nBeth posted a video recapping the latest Atlas Brew.\nSTAR ATLAS CAREER GUIDE\nAephia published an article about the careers in Star Atlas.\nStar Atlas Economic Report 2024 Q1\nStar Atlas published their latest economic report.",
